</div>


<div class="container-fluid bcolor p-4">
    <div class="row featurette d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading text-success text-center">FAQ's</h2>
            <ol class="list-group list-group-numbered lead">
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <b>Q1: Who are the sellers? </b><br>
                    Sellers are typically producers, farmers, and cooperatives of agricultural crops. All sellers are
                    verified by our platform through a seller-specific process, ensuring market-wide credibility.
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <b>Q2: Who are the buyers?</b><br> 
                    Buyers can be referred to as industrial buyers, whom may be crop processors, food manufactures, food
                    retailers, etc… All buyers are verified with a buyer specific process.
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <b>Q3: What is the platform's role?</b> <br> 
                    The platform serves as a marketplace, connecting buyers and sellers without acting as a broker or
                    intermediary.
                </li>
                <li class="list-group-item">
                    <b> Q4: How do I register? </b><br> 
                    To register, follow our simple sign-up process and complete the KYC verification.
                </li>
            </ol>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

